Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:04.58,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}coming for you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:12.58,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}all I ever wanted to do was do right things
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:15.09,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I never wanted to be the king,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:18.08,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I swear
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:22.37,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}all I ever wanted to do was save your life
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:25.05,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I never wanted to grab a knife,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:28.10,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I swear
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:32.93,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}tearless, fearless,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:35.89,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}burning, burning
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:38.95,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}you tell me what have I missed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:42.80,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}still wandering in the deep mist
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:48.63,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}if I lose it all, slip and fall
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:51.54,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I will never look away
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:57.80,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}if I lose it all, lose it all, lose it all
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:01.38,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}if I lose it all outside the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:04.76,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}live to die another day
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:10.47,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I don't want anything I'm just here to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:12.02,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Beware
