Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:52.42,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地鳴 地鳴 隆隆而至
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.42,0:06:54.52,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地鳴 地鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.19,0:06:58.49,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:04.58,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為你而來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:12.58,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只想做正確之事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:15.09,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我並不想稱王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:18.08,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:22.37,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只想拯救你的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:25.05,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我並不想拿起利刃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:28.10,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:32.93,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不流淚 不畏懼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:35.89,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃燒 燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:38.95,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你告訴我 我錯過了太多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:42.80,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}仍在濃霧中彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:48.63,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}若我失去一切 墜入深淵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:51.54,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我決不會逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:57.80,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}若我失去一切 失去一切 失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:01.38,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}若我在牆外失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:04.76,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我定將向死而生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:10.47,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我本不願立於此處
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:12.02,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:15.15,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地鳴 地鳴 隆隆而至
